1. Binance Alpha will launch CROSS, with a threshold of 140 points for airdrops;
2. Jupiter Studio: Anti-sniping protection supports users to set "sniping tax" on their own;
3. Analyst: Bitcoin bull market may end in October;
4. Slow Mist Cosine: The private key corresponding to the Sui address cannot derive the Aptos address of the same address, and the two cannot be converted;
5. Upbit lists STRIKE as a transaction warning project and will suspend deposit services;
6. Binance will launch BULLA and IDOL perpetual contracts;
7. Web3 cloud platform ICN completed 28.8 million euros in financing, with a valuation of 398 million euros, led by NGP Capital;
8. "Insider whale" once again increased its position by 43.19 BTC, worth 4.7 million US dollars;
9. Sonic Labs Lianchuang AC: A new version of the client that supports Gas subsidies will be launched soon;
10. Bitcoin's early whale transferred 10,000 BTC after 14 years of silence;
11. Cathie Wood: We are still in the Bitcoin bull market;
12. The central bank: Increase the replication and promotion of the "Shanghai experience", support the promotion of innovative applications of digital RMB to relevant free trade pilot zones;
13. Well-known ETH/BTC bull James Fickel deposited 80,000 ETH in Coinbase Prime, worth more than US$200 million;
14. A new wallet injected US$4.16 million USDC into HyperLiquid, and went long on HYPE with 10x leverage.
